languages.text: Молитва в корабельном святилище наполнила вас праведным рвением. Вперед, к победам во славу Империума!

languages.text: A prayer in the voidship's shrine has filled you with righteous fervour. Onward to victory for the glory of the Imperium!

languages.text: Una oración en el templo de la nave te llena de fervor justo. ¡A la victoria, por la gloria del Imperium!
languages.original_text: A prayer in the voidship's shrine has filled you with righteous fervour. Onward to victory for the glory of the Imperium!

languages.text: ヴォイドシップの神殿での祈りが、あなたたちを熱意で満たした。帝国の栄光のため、勝利に向かって前進せよ！
languages.original_text: A prayer in the voidship's shrine has filled you with righteous fervour. Onward to victory for the glory of the Imperium!

languages.text: 你在虚空舰的祭坛处祈祷，你的心里充满了正义的热情。为了帝国的荣耀，为了胜利，前进！
languages.original_text: A prayer in the voidship's shrine has filled you with righteous fervour. Onward to victory for the glory of the Imperium!

languages.text: Ein Gebet am Schrein des Raumschiffes hat dich mit einem rechtschaffenen Fieber erfüllt. Auf zum Sieg für den Ruhm des Imperiums!
languages.original_text: A prayer in the voidship's shrine has filled you with righteous fervour. Onward to victory for the glory of the Imperium!

languages.text: Une prière au sanctuaire du vaisseau vous a rempli de ferveur. En avant vers la victoire, pour la gloire de l'Imperium !
languages.original_text: A prayer in the voidship's shrine has filled you with righteous fervour. Onward to victory for the glory of the Imperium!

languages.text: Uçsuz gemisinin mabedinde edilen bir dua, seni erdemli bir coşkuyla doldurdu. İmparatorluk'un şanı için zafere doğru ilerle!
languages.original_text: A prayer in the voidship's shrine has filled you with righteous fervour. Onward to victory for the glory of the Imperium!
